WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.166
Hey, good morning everybody.

00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:05.388
I just wanted to come on here and tell you some more things the Lord has showed me in prayer time.

00:00:08.610 --> 00:00:14.340
I'll tell you some positive things, some good things, but I have to tell you this first, and this is not so good.

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:16.896
I want to be uplifting.

00:00:16.896 --> 00:00:24.735
I don't want to stir up fear or make anybody afraid, but I have to tell you what the Holy Spirit is telling me.

00:00:24.735 --> 00:00:30.539
There are things that we can avoid and some things I don't think we can.

00:00:30.750 --> 00:00:38.093
I feel I'm a watchman, like I've said, and it's my job to tell you what's going on.

00:00:38.093 --> 00:00:46.003
There was a massive barge traveling down the Mississippi River.

00:00:46.003 --> 00:00:50.649
I could see rust on the side of this barge; it was like a big boat.

00:00:51.197 --> 00:00:54.780
It was supposedly carrying grain or something out of the north somewhere.

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:58.140
There was black all around the top of it.

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:04.619
The area where the captain or the person who drives the boat sits was white and had rust on it.

00:01:04.619 --> 00:01:06.128
It looked like it was weathered.

00:01:06.128 --> 00:01:11.003
There was a little square opening on the deck part.

00:01:15.192 --> 00:01:24.780
They were moving, went out into the Gulf of Mexico, and turned their boat to face east.

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:28.884
They opened the hatch and put out a rocket.

00:01:28.884 --> 00:01:33.127
They lifted it up.

00:01:33.127 --> 00:01:45.900
The men on this boat were Asian; I have no idea if it was China or whatever, but they raised this rocket up.

00:01:48.495 --> 00:02:00.060
It was about five feet tall and probably about a foot to two feet thick at the most.

00:02:00.876 --> 00:02:08.378
It was black and white and had USSR written on the rocket.

00:02:08.835 --> 00:02:15.300
They shot the rocket out over America, and when they did, it exploded.

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:20.040
But I kept hearing in the spirit realm, 'It's not going to get high enough.

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:24.020
' That's what I was hearing.

00:02:25.209 --> 00:02:39.870
It went out over the Tennessee and Kentucky area, Atlanta, Mississippi, Alabama, and then it went up by Ohio and exploded right over all that area.

00:02:39.870 --> 00:02:48.017
When it did, it was an EMP, and the EMP turned out all the lights.

00:02:48.274 --> 00:03:01.740
Because it didn't get high enough, it didn't have a blast radius that affected everything way over to the west, but it affected all of Virginia and Pennsylvania.

00:03:04.483 --> 00:03:07.586
It was terrible; complete darkness was over this area.

00:03:09.154 --> 00:03:16.867
The further west you went, it wasn't as dark, and things weren't affected as badly.

00:03:16.867 --> 00:03:28.800
I could see that people in places like Colorado did not have cell phones, internet, or cable TV.

00:03:34.594 --> 00:03:42.334
They had TVs with bunny ears and landline telephones, and they still had electricity.

00:03:42.923 --> 00:03:49.073
You weren't able to have a whole bunch of stuff going; the power grid was really weak, but you were still able to power things.

00:03:50.620 --> 00:03:55.739
I don't understand it all; I just see things whenever I'm praying.

00:03:57.694 --> 00:04:00.353
I could see the emergency broadcast come on.

00:04:00.353 --> 00:04:04.286
I could hear it, and they were warning the people of what happened.

00:04:04.286 --> 00:04:10.371
You know how they warn you with the emergency broadcast alerts on our TVs?

00:04:13.174 --> 00:04:20.691
They ran that because it turned the TV on, and you could hear the emergency broadcast going off.

00:04:22.230 --> 00:04:28.220
I had some friends call the landline at my house, and they asked, 'Do you have power?

00:04:28.220 --> 00:04:30.300
' I said, 'Yes.

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:37.289
' I went to my refrigerator, opened it up, and there was still a light on inside.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:48.008
Looking out south, I could see in the spirit realm that the sycamore trees had leaves on them.

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:53.639
It was still really warm outside.

00:04:54.308 --> 00:05:11.070
Whenever I'm seeing in the spirit and the Lord is showing me something, I always try to pay attention to my surroundings: the trees, the weather, and the warmth outside, how it feels, you know, how I would have assumed it to feel, where the sun is at, everything.

00:05:11.070 --> 00:05:14.760
I try to pay attention because you can always tell where we are in the season.

00:05:16.329 --> 00:05:23.970
The sun was setting more towards the southwest, so it was a summer month, probably late summer.

00:05:26.733 --> 00:05:34.500
So, this was basically the end of it, but it was a warning of an EMP attack upon our nation.

00:05:39.159 --> 00:05:46.227
I know it's a heavy message, but I want to tell you about things that the Lord shows me to pray about.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:54.403
It's not to stir up fear; I believe we can stop things through intercessory prayer.

00:05:54.403 --> 00:05:58.979
I tell people this stuff to warn you to pray.

00:06:00.473 --> 00:06:02.490
Thank you so much for watching this video.

00:06:02.490 --> 00:06:04.873
Hopefully, it didn't freak you out too bad.

00:06:04.873 --> 00:06:08.180
Have a blessed day, everybody.
